c: 2
v: 118
t: "Oo kuwa aan waxba ogeyni waxay yidhaahdaan: Oo muxuu Allaah noola hadli waayey si toos ah ama calaamo ay noogu iman weydey? Weliba sidaas oo kale bay yidhaahdeen kuwii ka horreeyay, wax la mid ah hadalkooda oo kale, Quluubtooda baa dhammaan ah kuwa isa shabbaha. Xaqiiq Waxaanu uga dhignay Aayadaha caddaan dad iyagu yaqiinsan"